{{Infobox artwork | image_file =La Rivière by Aristide Maillol (Museum of Modern Art New York).jpg | painting_alignment = Front | image_size = 300px | title = La Rivière | alt = | other_language_1 = | other_title_1 = | other_language_2 = | other_title_2 = | artist = [[Aristide Maillol]] | year = 1938-39; completed 1943 | type = lead | height_metric = 136.5 | width_metric = | length_metric = | height_imperial = {{frac|53|3|4}} | width_imperial = 90 | length_imperial = 66 | metric_unit = cm | imperial_unit = in | city = various | museum = | coordinates = | owner = }}
'''''La Rivière''''' (''The River'') is a lead or bronze sculpture by [[Aristide Maillol]].<ref>[http://siris-artinventories.si.edu/ipac20/ipac.jsp?session=136V63805TD82.3743&profile=ariall&source=~!siartinventories&view=subscriptionsummary&uri=full=3100001~!426173~!12&ri=3&aspect=Keyword&menu=search&ipp=20&spp=20&staffonly=&term=+maillol&index=.GW&uindex=&aspect=Keyword&menu=search&ri=3&limitbox_1=LO01+=+ias "The River, (sculpture)."] ''SIRIS''</ref>
==Location== There are examples at the [[Tuileries Garden#The Jardin du Carrousel|Jardin du Carrousel]], [[Paris]];<ref>http://www.musee-orsay.fr/fr/collections/catalogue-des-oeuvres/notice.html?nnumid=6775</ref> [[Citygarden]], [[St. Louis, Missouri]]; [[Museum of Modern Art]], [[New York City]];<ref>http://www.moma.org/collection/object.php?object_id=81798</ref> the [[Norton Simon Museum]], [[Zurich]];<ref>http://www.nortonsimon.org/collections/browse_artist.php?name=Maillol%2C+Aristide&resultnum=10</ref> [[Kunsthalle Hamburg]], [[Hamburg]];<ref>http://artomaniak.blogspot.de/2012/10/merkwurdig-wie-man-immer-wieder-dingen.html</ref> and the [[Virginia Museum of Fine Arts]], [[Richmond, Virginia]].<ref>https://vmfa.museum/collections/art/la-riviere/</ref>
